                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">A comprehensive 45-day program to master the entire web development stack.</p>
                    <a href="/student-dashboard" class="inline-block w-full text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-blue-700">
