                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Learn to design beautiful and user-friendly interfaces with Figma.</p>
                    <a href="index.html" class="inline-block w-full text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-blue-700">
                        Start Learning
