            </div>

            <div class="card-bg rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02]">
                <img src="http://googleusercontent.com/images/autocad.jpg" alt="Course Thumbnail" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">AutoCAD & Engineering Design</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Master 2D and 3D design for engineering and architecture.</p>
